        """
        Return the matrix constructed from self using rows with indices in
        the rows list.

        EXAMPLES::

            sage: M = MatrixSpace(Integers(8),3,3)
            sage: A = M(range(9)); A
            [0 1 2]
            [3 4 5]
            [6 7 0]
